title: Oh, How Did You Find Our Show?
description: Everyone's back from vacation and Dave kicks the year off with a new joke, Dave tries to convince Jenny to do a medical treatment to something on her body, Spouse Holiday X Factor, Carson calls in to talk about being home for the holidays, War of the Roses, Jenny Has a Friend, and more!
